 Charli XCX 出演根据圣女贞德改编的电影https://www.nme.com/news/film/charli-xcx-cast-film-sacrifice-loosely-based-joan-of-arc-3810268?utm_source=rss&utm_medium=rss&utm_campaign=charli-xcx-cast-film-牺牲松散的圣女贞德Sophie ButcherWed, 06 Nov 2024 16:43:16 +0000 Film NewsMusic NewsNews https://www.nme.com/?p=3810268 <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="查理·XCX" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p>她加入了安雅·泰勒-乔伊、克里斯·埃文斯和容·林的行列</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/charli-xcx-cast-film-sacrifice-loosely-based-joan-of-arc-3810268">Charli XCX 出演的电影根据《圣女贞德》改编，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ; <p><img width="2000" height="1270" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice.jpg" class="attachment-full size-full wp-post-image" alt="查理·XCX" decoding="async" loading="lazy" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-400x254.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-800x508.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-696x442.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/11/Charli-xcx-sacrifice-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p> <a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/charli-xcx">Charli XCX</a>出演了一部大致受圣女贞德故事启发的电影。</p><p><b>阅读更多：</b> <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/julian-casablancas-working-with-charli-xcx-fame-has-never-hit-someone-better-time-3805745"><b>Julian Casablancas 谈与 Charli XCX 的合作：“名声从来没有在更好的时机袭击过一个人”</b></a></p><p>据<a href="https://deadline.com/2024/11/charli-xcx-yung-lean-join-chris-evans-aanya-taylor-joy-romain-gavras-movie-sacrifice-1236166511/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><i>Deadline</i></a>报道，查莉·XCX 已加入法国导演罗曼·加夫拉斯的英文处女作<i>《牺牲》</i>的演员阵容。她将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/anya-taylor-joy">安雅·泰勒-乔伊</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/furiosa-a-mad-max-saga"><i>《福瑞奥莎</i></a>》）、<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chris-evans">克里斯·埃文斯</a>（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/films/avengers-endgame"><i>《复仇者联盟：终局之战》</i></a> ）、文森特·卡塞尔（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/reviews-movie-11799-320528"><i>《黑天鹅》</i></a> ）和安比卡·莫德（ <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/tv-reviews/one-day-review-netflix-leo-woodall-david-nicholls-3583811"><i>《一日</i></a>》）一起主演。</p><p>剧情简介如下：《<i>牺牲</i>》——大致受到圣女贞德故事的启发——讲述了琼（泰勒-乔伊饰）的故事，她是一个热心的灵魂，受到只有她能听到的火山预言的驱使，她肩负着拯救世界的使命来自激烈的清算。</p><p> “她和她的神秘门徒民兵一起劫持了一场迷人的慈善晚会，并劫持了三名人质：迈克·泰勒（埃文斯饰），一位陷入困境、渴望救赎的电影明星，布雷肯（卡塞尔饰），世界首富，以及凯蒂（莫德饰），谁只是运气不好。他们被迫踏上穿越森林和大火的旅程，直到迈克面临终极问题：他会为人类牺牲什么？” </p><figure id="attachment_3802004" aria-describedby="caption-attachment-3802004" style="width: 2000px" class="wp-caption alignnone"><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="size-full wp-image-3802004" src="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe.jpg" alt="Charli XCX 在 Storm King 艺术中心摆姿势。亨利·雷德克利夫信用" width="2000" height="1600" srcset="https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe.jpg 2000w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-400x320.jpg 400w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-800x640.jpg 800w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-696x557.jpg 696w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-1392x1114.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2024/10/Charli-XCX-posing-at-Storm-King-Arts-Center.-Credit-Henry-Redcliffe-1068x854.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /><figcaption id="caption-attachment-3802004" class="wp-caption-text"> Charli XCX 在 Storm King 艺术中心摆姿势。亨利·雷德克利夫信用</figcaption></figure><p>目前正在希腊和保加利亚拍摄的电影中，Charli XCX 的角色细节尚未得到证实。</p><p>在宣布的其他配角成员中，瑞典说唱歌手<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/yung-lean">Yung Lean</a>是他的电影处女作，他还与 XCX 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/robyn">Robyn</a>合作混音了她的歌曲“360”。</p><p> Charli XCX 目前有 6 个银幕项目正在进行中，包括格雷格·荒木 (Gregg Araki) 的《<i>我想要你的性</i>》和由<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/emma-corrin-reveals-the-deadpool-wolverine-death-that-made-them-feel-so-bad-3780930">艾玛·科林</a>( <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/deadpool-wolverine-review-marvel-3777877"><i>《死侍》和《金刚狼》</i></a> ) 和<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/maika-monroe-details-first-time-seeing-nicolas-cage-in-longlegs-makeup-3775626">麦卡·梦露</a>( <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/film-reviews/longlegs-review-nicolas-cage-maika-monroe-horror-3774136"><i>《长腿</i></a>》) 领衔的图画小说改编版《<i>英雄百夜</i>》。</p><p>此外，本月晚些时候，XCX 被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-confirmed-as-host-and-performer-on-snl-next-month-oh-fuck-3808467">确认担任<i>SNL</i>的主持人和表演者</a>。</p><p>她还将与<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/chappell-roan">Chappell Roan</a>和<a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/sabrina-carpenter">Sabrina Carpenter</a>一起成为明年<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/charli-xcx-says-she-chappell-roan-and-sabrina-carpenter-headlining-primavera-sound-2025-is-the-holy-trinity-3806307">Primavera Sound 2025 的主角</a>。最近，随着她的专辑<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-review-lyrics-tracklist-3762875">《Brat》</a>和混音版本<a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/album/charli-xcx-brat-and-its-completely-different-but-also-still-brat-review-a-masterpiece-in-the-art-of-club-music-curatorship-3802412">《Brat And It&#39;s Completely Different But Also Still Brat》</a>取得巨大成功，<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/brat-chosen-as-collins-dictionary-word-of-the-year-3808604">柯林斯词典选择“brat”作为 2024 年年度词汇</a>。</p><p>后<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/charli-xcx-cast-film-sacrifice-loosely-based-joan-of-arc-3810268">Charli XCX 出演的电影根据《圣女贞德》改编，</a>首先出现在<a href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a>上。</p> ;
